This paper deals with the problem of Vision and Language Navigation, which involves navigating through a previously unseen environment based on natural language instructions and photo-realistic image views. This problem is at the intersection of computer vision, natural language processing, and robotics. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.RO (Robotics).
